parameters: \n<Philip>Lo-Loban is gone! What is going on?
\n<Zarie>I don't think gargoyles can do this!
\n<Dwayne>Looks like an attack... of an army.
\n<Zarie>Those bandits! I think they are the one who did this!
\n<Zarie>I mean, gargoyles are evil, but they will not
spend time to do this kind of thing.
\n<Philip>I agree! As soon as we finished those gargoyles,
we should take care of these bandits.
\n<Dwayne>Let's save your sister and my mother, then we'll
make these bandits regret what they've done.
\n<Dwayne>Let's find another way, we cannot cross that bridge.
\n<Zarie>Before we leave, let's find for survivors.
\n<Zarie>I still feel someone out there is still alive.
\n<Zarie>I still feel someone out there is still alive.
